comments: Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact to Ayton (PHX) during his put-back shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Carter's (PHX) path and makes marginal contact during the off-ball screen.
Carter (PHX) has a marginal resting hand to Adebayo's (MIA) lower body and makes clean ball contact with the other as he contests the shot attempt in the lane.
Rubio (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Iguodala's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) is in a slightly wide screening position when he makes marginal contact with Carter (PHX) during the off-ball screen.
Bridges (PHX) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Robinson (MIA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Crowder (MIA) makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) in the lane.
Booker (PHX) reaches over Adebayo's (MIA) shoulder and makes contact with his hand while it is in contact with the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Ayton (PHX).
Ayton (PHX) jumps A to B and makes contact to Robinson's (MIA) body after the release that affects his jump shot attempt.
Olynyk (MIA) is established in Carter's (PHX) path during the off-ball screen and makes marginal contact.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of defensive goaltending is confirmed. Adebayo (MIA) makes contact with the ball as it is on a downward trajectory toward the basket.
Olynyk (MIA) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
